Dynatrace AppMon enables in-depth, end-to-end monitoring of applications running on Pivotal Cloud Foundry, via an embedded agent or by being bundled with the application. The agent collects tracing and monitoring data, and publishes the resulting performance metrics and other details to Dynatrace AppMon dashboards.  

